71
00:09:07,539 --> 00:09:15,950
And while this discourse is being spoken, there arose in the Venerable Kandanya the dust-free, stainless vision of the Dhamma.

72
00:09:16,671 --> 00:09:20,956
Whatever is subject to arising is all subject to ceasing.

73
00:09:22,577 --> 00:09:25,402
