74
00:09:26,022 --> 00:09:28,445
Kandanya has really understood.

75
00:09:28,504 --> 00:09:30,967
Kandanya has really understood.

76
00:09:31,788 --> 00:09:34,812
And that's how Venerable Kandanya became known as

